Even on moonlander i use palm to press corner button of the board instead of pinky.
Palm is independent from fingers too! 2 Independent bits!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://shop.keyboard.io/cdn/shop/files/m100-for-web.jpg?v=1706306369&amp;amp;width=360&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
